<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <%= form_for @covenant_form, :html => {:multipart => true} do |f| %>
                  <% if @covenant_form.errors.any? %>
                    <div id="error_explanation">
                      <h2><%= pluralize(@covenant_form.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this covenant_form from being saved:</h2>

                      <ul>
                      <% @covenant_form.errors.full_messages.each do |msg| %>
                        <li><%= msg %></li>
                      <% end %>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                  <p>Salkehatchie Summer Service is committed to providing a safe and secure environment for all children, youth, vulnerable adults, and volunteers who participate in its ministries. The following policy .statements reflect my commitment to preserving Salkehatchie Summer Service as a holy place of safety and protection for all who would participate and as a place in which all people can experience the love of God through relationships with others.
                  </p><p>
1. No adults who have been convicted of child abuse (either sexual abuse, physical abuse, or emotional abuse) should volunteer to work with Salkehatchie Summer Service.<br/>
2. Volunteers shall observe the "Two-Adult Rule" at all times so that no adult is ever alone with youth.<br/>
3. Volunteers shall attend regular, training and educational events provided by the camp director(s) to keep informed of .policies and state laws regarding child abuse.<br/>
4. Volunteers shall immediately report any behavior that seems abusive or inappropriate to the camp director.<br/>
</p>
                  <div class="field">
                    <%= f.check_box :policy %> 1. As a volunteer, do you agree to observe and abide by all policies regarding working in ministries with children and youth?
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <%= f.check_box :two_adult %> 2. As a volunteer, do you agree to observe the "Two-Adult Rule" at all times?
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <%= f.check_box :training %> 3. As a volunteer, do you agree to participate in training and education events related to your volunteer assignment if required?
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <%= f.check_box :report_abuse %> 4. As a volunteer, do you agree to promptly report abusive or inappropriate behavior to the camp director?
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <%= f.check_box :child_abuse %> 5. As a volunteer, do you agree to inform the camp director if you have ever been convicted of child abuse?
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <%= f.check_box :agree_to_covenant %> I have read this Participant Covenant, and I agree to observe and abide by the policies set forth above.
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <% if @covenant_form.user_signature %>
                      Current Signature<br/>
                      <%= image_tag @covenant_form.user_signature_url.to_s, :class => "thmb" %>
                    <% end %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <%= f.label :user_signature %><br>
                    <%= f.file_field :user_signature %>
                  </div>

                  <div class="actions">
                    <%= f.submit :class => "btn btn-default col-md-3", style:"height:40px" %>
                  </div>
                <% end %>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>